name: ❤️ Frida Punk 082 - FridaLove ❤️
description: Frida's Take on Love: “Nothing compares to your hands, nothing like the green-gold of your eyes. My body is filled with you for days and days. You are the mirror of the night. The violent flash of lightning. The dampness of the earth. The hollow of your armpits is my shelter. My fingers touch your blood.” - Frida Kahlo
